4Geeks Academy offers a Course in Applied Artificial Intelligence designed for professionals seeking to integrate AI into their work. This six-week program requires no prior knowledge and includes two live online classes per week, capped at 12 participants. Students will explore AI applications across various industries, focusing on generative AI, context, prompts, and models, ensuring they are equipped to implement AI effectively in their roles. Upon completion, participants receive an official certificate recognized by multiple institutions. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop